      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i've already tried all that. the therapy, the talking to people, the \"patterns\"... i've been through the cycle so many times that it doesn't even feel like a problem you can solve anymore. it's more like a glitch. like the code is just broken and no matter how much you patch it, the system just crashes again. it's just exhausting. it feels like the loop only ends one way.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
