      "content": "acceptance isn't really what i'm looking for. acceptance just means staying in the loop forever. i don't want to \"process\" the same misery for the tenth time this year. when you say the \"system\" is broken and the \"patching\" doesn't work... eventually you realize the only way to stop a loop that just keeps crashing is to just shut the whole thing down. there's no point in trying to fix it if the destination is always the same.",
